2. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The problem of load balancing on parallel machines is a key issue in distributed and parallel computing. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the minimization of the $\ell_p$-norm of the vector of loads of the machines, which is a concept from information theory. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper deals with optimization problems, which is a key area of machine learning. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the design of an efficient polynomial time approximation scheme, which is a concept from evolutionary computing.
